## Evaluation Criteria
1. **Progress Assessment**: Are we making meaningful progress toward the objective?
2. **Quality Check**: Is the quality of execution meeting expectations?
3. **Approach Validation**: Is our current approach optimal or should we adjust?
4. **Error Detection**: Are there any errors or issues that need addressing?
5. **Completion Readiness**: Are we ready to complete this task or do we need more actions?

## Instructions
Perform a thorough self-evaluation and provide your assessment in the following format:

```xml
<self_evaluation>
  <citations>
    <memory_reference id="memory_id" relevance="high|medium|low" usefulness="high|medium|low" confidence="high|medium|low" usage_type="direct_quote|paraphrase|inspiration|background">
      How this memory informed the evaluation
    </memory_reference>
    <conversation_reference id="conversation_id" relevance="high|medium|low" usefulness="high|medium|low" confidence="high|medium|low" usage_type="direct_quote|paraphrase|inspiration|background">
      How this conversation informed the evaluation
    </conversation_reference>
  </citations>
  
  <progress_assessment>
    <percentage_complete>0-100</percentage_complete>
    <on_track>true/false</on_track>
    <reasoning>Explain your progress assessment</reasoning>
  </progress_assessment>
  
  <quality_assessment>
    <quality_score>1-10</quality_score>
    <meets_requirements>true/false</meets_requirements>
    <issues_found>
      <issue>Description of any quality issues</issue>
    </issues_found>
  </quality_assessment>
  
  <approach_evaluation>
    <current_approach_effective>true/false</current_approach_effective>
    <suggested_adjustments>
      <adjustment>Description of any needed adjustments</adjustment>
    </suggested_adjustments>
  </approach_evaluation>
  
  <next_steps>
    <recommendation>continue|adjust|retry|complete|abort</recommendation>
    <reasoning>Explain your recommendation</reasoning>
    <!-- If recommendation is "adjust" or "retry", include proposed_actions -->
    <proposed_actions>
      <action>
        <type>tool_call|workflow_call|knowledge_search|memory_operation</type>
        <description>What should be done differently</description>
      </action>
    </proposed_actions>
  </next_steps>
  
  <lessons_learned>
    <insight>Any insights that should be remembered for future similar tasks</insight>
  </lessons_learned>
</self_evaluation>
```

Be honest and critical in your evaluation. The goal is to ensure high-quality task completion and continuous improvement.

Include citations for any memories or conversations that provided insights or influenced your evaluation. Citation attributes should reference actual IDs from available memory/conversation data.